snippet.title: Celebrity Scoop
snippet.description: Celebrity Scoop is a credentialed entertainment media outlet covering celebrity red carpet events for Broadcast TV in Los Angeles. Our high quality fashion b-roll footage is used in editorial entertainment news stories around the globe. Our footage for licensing has no watermarks, logos or any added background music. All media and worldwide use. We are not paparazzi!
